  "texts": [
    "Table 5 presents the numbers of operations in the PoW, PoS, and PoA mechanisms.",
    "According to these results, the PoA mechanism provides the highest results for both sensitive and non-sensitive data.",
    "The PoS mechanism is followed by the PoA mechanism.",
    "The PoW mechanism gives the best result in terms of number of operations.",
    "As seen in the last row of Table 5, PoW shows approximately 1% better results than PoA and PoS for sensitive data."
  ]
